      • usePrimitiveArrayConstants

        public IR2ProConverter usePrimitiveArrayConstants(boolean usePrimitiveArrayConstants)
        Specifies whether PrimitiveArrayConstants can be generated, when applicable.

        If they are generated then they should be converted back to standard Java arrays before converting to Java class files using PrimitiveArrayConstantReplacer.
